cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.GR

This paper involves the use of deep learning methods for remote sensing applications, specifically for the retrieval of chlorophyll-a from sea surface reflectance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.GR (Graphics).
